column5: Guys, I need your help, my Eagle Fish Elite fish finder stopped working, I checked everything that could be wrong but still no go.  Would you happen to know where could I get it fixed in the GTA ?  Thanks a lot
Try going to their website and go to FAQ and trouble shooting you may get some help. GOOD LUCK
Angling Outfitters in Woodstock. Nobody knows more than Joslin. But if it's new, take it back were you bought it.
depending on the model the eagles had cheap quality power supply's in them may not be worth fixin, hopefully under warranty
